## SECTION 8: Polymarket as intelligence honeypot — 71 minutes of warning

Prediction markets have become an inadvertent intelligence tool during this conflict, with documented insider trading patterns providing a **measurable early-warning window** that ranges from 12 minutes to several hours before classified information becomes public.

